text:
Nathaël Julan (16 July 1996 – 3 January 2020) was a French professional footballer. He played as a forward.
Julan was born in Montivilliers and was from a Guadeloupean background. In June 2016, he signed his first professional contract with Le Havre. He was last signed for Ligue 2 side Guingamp.
On 3 January 2020, Julan was killed in a car accident in Pordic. He was 23.
